{"tid":1179312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊：刑恐、性罪行被剔除　感可惜但理解","createTime":"2019-05-31T04:37:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T07:44:37.000Z","uid":60281,"like":5,"dislike":143,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"4d4d24224318579d804c18d8d0e98fcbcde49633","tid":1179312,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/18238812_10154715499169685_807109129761211439_o_LE8Uf_dvAVp_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F18238812_10154715499169685_807109129761211439_o_LE8Uf_dvAVp_1200x0.png&h=d457d1ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n保安局局長李家超今日宣布，進一步將《逃犯條例》修訂的引渡門檻提高至可判七年或以上的罪行。行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊向《立場新聞》表示，對政府做法感到可惜，認為這將會剔除刑事恐嚇、性罪行等嚴重罪行。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊今日接受《立場新聞》訪問時，對政府提高引渡門檻感到可惜，指被剔除的都是嚴重且社會關心的罪行，包括是刑事恐嚇、槍械管制相關的罪行，「性罪行，對於未成年的保障，亦是重要的罪行，如果要剔除這些罪行，都是令人感到可惜的」。<br />\n<br />\n但他指剔除罪行能夠釋除部分港人疑慮，令草案更有把握獲通過，認為這是政府要面對的政治現實，對此表示理解。他又指新措施加入公平審訊要求，照顧犯人基本權益，認為社會應該會歡迎。李家超提出只處理由國家中央政府提出的請求，以內地為例就是只處理由最高人民檢察院提出移交要求。被問到台灣是否存有「中央機構」，湯家驊認為這其實意指「每個司法管轄區最高層次」的機構，坦言「中央機構」用詞不太貼切，但相信不會存在由大陸決定台灣移交申請的情況。<br />\n<br />\n李家超今日宣布為了釋除疑慮，提出三方面共六項措施，包括在將罪行引渡門檻提高至七年或以上；可按個別情況需要，於協定加入無罪假定、公開審訊、有律師代表、不強迫認罪等要求；只處理由當地中央政府提出的請求；以及在條例草案通過後，與內地討論讓港人申請回港服刑等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/逃犯條例-移交門檻增至七年-湯家驊-刑恐-性罪行被剔除-感可惜但理解/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%A7%BB%E4%BA%A4%E9%96%80%E6%AA%BB%E5%A2%9E%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%83%E5%B9%B4-%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A-%E5%88%91%E6%81%90-%E6%80%A7%E7%BD%AA%E8%A1%8C%E8%A2%AB%E5%89%94%E9%99%A4-%E6%84%9F%E5%8F%AF%E6%83%9C%E4%BD%86%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%2F&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoDbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=caeb0ded\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%A7%BB%E4%BA%A4%E9%96%80%E6%AA%BB%E5%A2%9E%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%83%E5%B9%B4-%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A-%E5%88%91%E6%81%90-%E6%80%A7%E7%BD%AA%E8%A1%8C%E8%A2%AB%E5%89%94%E9%99%A4-%E6%84%9F%E5%8F%AF%E6%83%9C%E4%BD%86%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%2F&h=53ead1e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/逃犯條例-移交門檻增至七年-湯家驊-刑恐-性罪行被剔除-感可惜但理解/</a>"},{"pid":"05a2e299305518c345247a689a2e923ad736da5d","tid":1179312,"uid":70786,"like":140,"dislike":1,"score":139,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:38:07.000Z","msg":"選擇性公義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0719971cffc365c92e9200a34aaf14268a324de3","tid":1179312,"uid":46042,"like":91,"dislike":0,"score":91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:38:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=GLyZFiCTq-M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGLyZFiCTq-M%C5%92LIHKG%C5%92&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoDbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=3f4f90f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=GLyZFiCTq-M</a><a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=GLyZFiCTq-M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGLyZFiCTq-M&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoDbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=39083667\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=GLyZFiCTq-M</a>"},{"pid":"5ffeda73e6db2e1ea3edf6af90690640834af0e7","tid":1179312,"uid":67500,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:38:30.000Z","msg":"廢老傳聲筒，講野冇乜價值"},{"pid":"5d4dc160e37168fc82d49f9bbc9bbbeb7d2b644b","tid":1179312,"uid":37413,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:38:44.000Z","msg":"香港變成性罪行逃犯天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748c1247c31b0685363dc68fb7b64e3929f665dc","tid":1179312,"ui